Baybay Silay:
Baybayin rule: Kung anong bigkas, siyang baybay.
Baybayin rule(en): What would be the phrase, it must be the characters.
Added: You've must translate the word from the language to tagalog (e.g: Teacher -> Guro).
Another: If you want to use the baybayin characters as your facebook name, just don't use Ra as part of the name, it is still invalid in unicode names.
Script version : B18+ (Added Ra)

